msgid ""
"This article describes how to get ROS 2 running on IBM Cloud using Docker"
" files. It first gives a brief overview of docker images and how they "
"work locally and then explores IBM Cloud and how the user can deploy "
"their containers on it. Afterwards, a short description of how the user "
